<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.7">
<l>māṉēy maṭanōk kitiṟat tetirvanta</l>
<l>vāṉēḻ viṭaiceṟ ṟavaṇi varaittōḷā</l>
<l>tēṉē tiruvēṅ kaṭamā malaimēya</l>
<l>kōṉē yeṉmaṉam kuṭikoṇ ṭiruntāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with beautiful boulder[-like] arms who killed seven bulls</l>
<l>Which came opposing [you], [all] for a doe-like simple glance,</l>
<l>Nectar, king who dwells on the great mountain Tiruvēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>You have taken my heart [for a] home.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
